###  http://www.cgiraldolo.com/highrisk-meddev-&-invitrodev-diag#manufacturerCompetentAuth
:manufacturerCompetentAuth rdf:type owl:DatatypeProperty ;
                           rdfs:domain :Manufacturer ;
                           rdfs:range rdfs:Literal .


###  http://www.cgiraldolo.com/highrisk-meddev-&-invitrodev-diag#manufacturerContactEmail
:manufacturerContactEmail rdf:type owl:DatatypeProperty ;
                          rdfs:domain :Manufacturer ;
                          rdfs:range xsd:string .


